Here is a Wall Street Journal story about leveraged single-stock exchange-t=
raded funds, which are like, instead of buying Nvidia Corp. stock, you can =
buy an ETF that gives you Nvidia=E2=80=99s daily returns multiplied by 2, o=
r negative 2. Intuitively, you know and I know and everyone knows what that=
