h higher,=E2=80=9D Vreeland said.
And it quotes the people involved in building the product saying no no no n=
o no no you=E2=80=99ve got it all wrong, this isn=E2=80=99t=C2=A0gambling, =
why would you even think that:

GraniteShares Chief Executive Will Rhind estimates about half of his single=
-stock ETF investors are individuals. Other investors include hedge funds t=
hat use momentum trading strategies and those looking for an arbitrage oppo=
rtunity between options, futures, ETFs and the underlying stock.=C2=A0
Rhind said the growing inflows and trading volumes this year are =E2=80=9Cv=
indication=E2=80=9D that there is demand for single-stock leveraged product=
