..
Matthew Tuttle, CEO of Tuttle Capital Management who partnered with fund ma=
nager Rex Shares on the T-REX single-stock funds, says he has been pleasant=
ly surprised by the growth this year.=C2=A0
=E2=80=9CI think this is going to become its own little ecosystem,=E2=80=9D=
 Tuttle said. =E2=80=9CI know there=E2=80=99s a lot of criticism of it. To =
me, it=E2=80=99s a tool.=E2=80=9D

It=E2=80=99s fine, it=E2=80=99s fine, it=E2=80=99s fun to have fun, but you=
