e around, almost nobody is pretending the endeavor is about anything other =
than =E2=80=98number go up.=E2=80=99=E2=80=9D <a href=3D"https://link.mail.=
bloombergbusiness.com/click/35310612.256343/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmN=
vbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDQtMjIvdGhlLXNlY3JldC10cmFkZS13YXMtb3B0aW=
