nV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yNDA1MDgmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5=
c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB7ee303d9" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=
=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: =
none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; bo=
rder-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">I quibbled</a>:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Well, everyone is=C2=A0<em>pretend=
ing</em>. =E2=80=A6 That=E2=80=99s what=E2=80=99s so weird about all of thi=
s.=C2=A0If you are a meme-stock executive or a crypto venture capitalist or=
 Robinhood, you can=E2=80=99t just go on TV and say =E2=80=9Cyes gambling i=
s fun and legal and we are probabilistically charging people a market-clear=
ing price for entertainment.=E2=80=9D You have to talk about how your meme =
stock is the future of free speech or how crypto is the future of ownership=
 or how retail options trading is the future of retirement savings. =E2=80=
=9CThis is all legitimate economic activity,=E2=80=9D you have to say, beca=
use people are still not entirely used to the idea that gambling is legitim=
ate economic activity.</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here is a <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombe=
rgbusiness.com/click/35310612.256343/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9maW5hbmNlL2=
