rder-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: =
solid; background-color: #ccc;">Wall Street Journal story</a> about leverag=
ed single-stock exchange-traded funds, which are like, instead of buying Nv=
idia Corp. stock, you can buy an ETF that gives you Nvidia=E2=80=99s daily =
returns multiplied by 2, or negative 2. Intuitively, you know and I know an=
