data provider VettaFi.</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And it quotes a customer saying that:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CI want to take advantage =
of high volatility situations. Any time I can trade leverage, automatically=
 my potential return on investment is much higher,=E2=80=9D Vreeland said.<=
/p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And it quotes the people involved in building =
the product saying no no no no no no you=E2=80=99ve got it all wrong, this =
isn=E2=80=99t=C2=A0<em>gambling</em>, why would you even think that:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">GraniteShares Chief Executive Will Rhind estim=
ates about half of his single-stock ETF investors are individuals. Other in=
vestors include hedge funds that use momentum trading strategies and those =
looking for an arbitrage opportunity between options, futures, ETFs and the=
 underlying stock.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Rhind said the growing inflows and trading vol=
umes this year are =E2=80=9Cvindication=E2=80=9D that there is demand for s=
ingle-stock leveraged products.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CFundamentally we=E2=80=99re trying to=
 democratize margin investing and access to margin. For a lot of investors =
these make sense because it=E2=80=99s much cheaper than using a margin acco=
unt,=E2=80=9D Rhind said. ...</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Matthew Tuttle, CEO of Tuttle Capital Manageme=
nt who partnered with fund manager Rex Shares on the T-REX single-stock fun=
ds, says he has been pleasantly surprised by the growth this year.=C2=A0</p=
>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CI think this is going to become its o=
wn little ecosystem,=E2=80=9D Tuttle said. =E2=80=9CI know there=E2=80=99s =
a lot of criticism of it. To me, it=E2=80=99s a tool.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">It=E2=80=99s fine, it=E2=80=99s fine, it=E2=80=
=99s fun to have fun, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/cl=
