_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-b=
ottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid;=
 background-color: #ccc;">Maybe that=E2=80=99s something</a>?</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Early this year, a struggling soccer team in P=
ortugal=E2=80=99s second division unveiled a new player to help in its batt=
le against relegation. He didn=E2=80=99t look like anyone=E2=80=99s idea of=
 a star signing.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Courtney Reum is a middle-aged American ventur=
e capitalist whose soccer career peaked a couple of decades earlier, when h=
e played for Columbia in the Ivy League.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That didn=E2=80=99t prevent Reum from earning =
a contract with L=C3=A4nk FC Vilaverdense. On Jan. 31, the final day of Eur=
opean soccer=E2=80=99s midseason transfer window, the club confirmed the fo=
rmer Goldman Sachs investment banker as the newest member of its squad.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Vilaverdense took a chance on Reum=E2=80=94ent=
iced by more than his sports skills. Reum=E2=80=99s deal with the team incl=
uded a loan, described as in the six figures, to ease the club=E2=80=99s fi=
nancial pressure, as well as potential future investment and access to Reum=
=E2=80=99s extensive business and finance network. =E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In the waning minutes of Vilaverdense=E2=80=99=
s crucial game against Torreense, Reum jogged onto the pitch for his pro de=
but.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CIt hasn=E2=80=99t quite sunk in,=E2=
=80=9D Reum said afterward. =E2=80=9CI genuinely felt great out there. I fe=
lt like I could do something.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">He did not, and they were relegated, but he ha=
d fun, and I suppose the money will help them in the third division.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"><a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness=
