#000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Elsewhere</a>=
:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Groups of private equity investors may soon be=
 allowed to buy as much as 30% of National Football League franchises.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Proposals under discussion would let buyout fi=
rms individually acquire as much 10% of a team, according to people familia=
r with the matter, who asked not to be identified because the deliberations=
 are confidential.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A special NFL committee is meeting to examine =
the league=E2=80=99s ownership rules. Talks are ongoing and the percentages=
 may change, some of the people said. A spokesperson for the NFL declined t=
o comment.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I am going to be very disappointed if, by 2027=
, the New York Jets do not have a quarterback on loan from Apollo.</p>
